We’ve made some updates to improve your delivery experience!
* Check out the new Account section that replaces Settings where you'll find features like your delivery region map.

* Check out the new Account section that replaces Settings where you'll find features like your delivery region map.

* We're introducing a better experience when having to return items. If an order is eligible, follow the prompts and you'll get a bonus for making the return trip.
* Updates based on new regulations in California.
